headline: Abbott Agrees to Global Continuous Glucose Monitoring Litigation Settlement with Dexcom
summary: ABBOTT PARK - Abbott announced today it has reached an agreement with DexCom, Inc. to settle all outstanding patent disputes between the companies in cases related to continuous glucose monitoring...
